mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: SQUARE DANCES "Ends Turn In", "Bachelor's Mill", "California, Here I Come", "Veleta No. 1", and "Veleta No. 2". SPECIAL FEATURES "The Big Event", "Ten Years of DO C DO", "They Followed the Square Dance Trail", "Square Dance Family Fun", and "Meet Our Guest Caller". REGULAR FEATURES "As I See It", "Events Seen Thru the Square Dancer's Eye", "Help! For Your Square Dance Club", "The Square of the Month: Herb Lesher", "'Round the Outside Ring", "The Green Sheet", "From the Floor", "On the Record", and "Calendar of Square Dance Events".
